          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript used for contemplation and study and is a treatise and an ancient textbook on mathematic as derived from planetary movements. The work, also referred to as the Vāsanābhāṣya, is possibly a commentary on the Siddhānta-śiromaṇi or, the Crown jewel of treatises, by the same author.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
